<i>We sure as hell don't get</i>
<i>a return on our investment.</i>

09:35.943 --> 09:38.490
<i>If they put a prayer room</i>
<i>in that new mall, folks,</i>

09:38.490 --> 09:39.909
<i>guess what...</i>

09:39.909 --> 09:41.663
[engine rumbling]

09:41.663 --> 09:44.627
<i>They're smart, these folks,</i>
<i>and we've been stupid.</i>

09:44.627 --> 09:46.881
<i>And now they're taking it all.</i>

09:46.881 --> 09:49.512
<i>Not just our business either.</i>
<i>Our land.</i>

