BILLY: Where's your weekly?
‐ Here you go.

10:20.449 --> 10:22.495
‐ You, give it up.

10:23.705 --> 10:25.834
BILLY: Pay up.
SHOP OWNER: Here.

10:27.128 --> 10:28.882
‐ Let's go.
Rent.

10:28.882 --> 10:30.385
‐ [laughing]

10:32.556 --> 10:34.977
[cash register dings]
[drawer clatters]

10:38.485 --> 10:41.198
The fuck's this?
‐ This is my two weeks' notice.

10:41.198 --> 10:44.622
I'll be closing down.
I'm moving to Abdi's new mall.

10:44.622 --> 10:46.835
BILLY: You, too,
you piece of shit?

10:46.835 --> 10:49.005
‐ Keep the money.

10:49.005 --> 10:51.009
‐ Please, Ace,
I pay what I owe.

10:51.009 --> 10:53.055
ACE: Oh, no, Naji.

10:53.055 --> 10:55.853
