11:13.805 --> 11:15.809
ACE: [yelling]
Is that that piece of shit?

11:15.809 --> 11:18.063
Get the fuck out of my way.

11:18.063 --> 11:20.611
Touch me again,
you fucking rake!

11:20.611 --> 11:22.531
Touch me again!
MAN: You need to step back.

11:22.531 --> 11:24.827
‐ Abdi, get the fuck out here!

11:24.827 --> 11:27.499
You fucking prick.

11:27.499 --> 11:29.462
ABDI: Hey.

11:29.462 --> 11:31.674
Looking to rent a stall?

11:31.674 --> 11:33.595
Get of your own shitty mall?

11:33.595 --> 11:35.557
We can help you with that.

11:35.557 --> 11:37.143
We have friends
and family rate.

11:37.143 --> 11:38.521
‐ You're not my fucking family,

11:38.521 --> 11:40.525
and you never were,
you adopted piece of shit.

11:40.525 --> 11:42.236
‐ Hey, hey, hey.
Back up. Back up.

11:42.236 --> 11:45.034
ABDI:
It's just business, right?
That's what Pop taught me.

11:45.034 --> 11:46.579
ACE: You know why
you got this land?

11:46.579 --> 11:48.040
'Cause no one else
fucking wants it.

11:48.040 --> 11:49.377
HASSAN: Haunted, right?

11:49.377 --> 11:51.631
Ghosts of the white people
who used to live here?

11:51.631 --> 11:52.800
ABDI: Who were those?

11:52.800 --> 11:55.931
The witches
or the slave owners?

11:55.931 --> 11:59.145
ACE: Stop poaching my tenants.
‐ Hey, hey, hey.

11:59.145 --> 12:01.734
‐ Go back to your fucking car.

