13:36.214 --> 13:38.636
‐ You give that landlord
two lanes.

13:38.636 --> 13:40.599
You understand?

13:46.067 --> 13:47.153
JOY: Why?

13:47.153 --> 13:49.575
He seems okay.

13:49.575 --> 13:51.119
