13:53.206 --> 13:55.962
‐ After the accident,
he didn't even charge us
to tow the car.

13:55.962 --> 13:57.173
‐ Exactly.

13:57.173 --> 13:58.801
Nothing's for free
with a man like that,

13:58.801 --> 14:00.179
