14:00.179 --> 14:01.891
‐ Mom.
‐ Joy.

14:01.891 --> 14:05.105
If you can't see how
that dirty bird's been
looking at us...

14:05.105 --> 14:08.195
[sighs]
I haven't taught you anything.

14:09.615 --> 14:11.702
JOY: Are you okay?

14:11.702 --> 14:14.207
You seem a little...

14:14.207 --> 14:16.629
you know.

14:16.629 --> 14:18.883
‐ This isn't about me.

14:20.720 --> 14:22.766
‐ You know, if‐‐if you're not
feeling like yourself,

14:22.766 --> 14:25.145
you can tell me.

14:25.145 --> 14:28.611
I just mean, you haven't
had your medicine
in a week, right?

14:28.611 --> 14:30.949
‐ I'm getting more pills
at the hospital today.

14:30.949 --> 14:34.581
Don't you worry one little bit.

14:34.581 --> 14:36.836
[lock clicks, handle rattles]

14:36.836 --> 14:39.800
‐ After I finish school stuff,
can I go to the store?

14:41.052 --> 14:43.265
To get more drawing paper.

14:43.265 --> 14:45.060
‐ I got you some two towns ago.

14:45.060 --> 14:47.482
We're not millionaires, Joy.

14:47.482 --> 14:51.031
‐ I don't know, I'm just‐‐
I'm feeling a little
cabin‐fevery.

14:51.031 --> 14:53.035
I haven't been out of the house
in a week.

14:53.035 --> 14:55.330
‐ Little love...

14:55.330 --> 14:56.834
<i>[tense music]</i>

14:56.834 --> 15:00.425
This town is not a good place.

15:00.425 --> 15:02.679
Not just that dirty bird.

15:02.679 --> 15:04.307
He's the roach you can see.

15:04.307 --> 15:06.269
The rest are in the walls.

15:06.269 --> 15:08.273
I've heard things.

15:08.273 --> 15:10.069
Massacres.

15:10.069 --> 15:13.075
Kids vanishing into thin air.

15:13.075 --> 15:15.162
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:15.162 --> 15:17.208
‐ Okay, Mom.

15:17.208 --> 15:20.381
ANNIE: Just a couple more days.

15:20.381 --> 15:23.846
We'll get the car fixed
good as new.

15:23.846 --> 15:27.437
We'll be back on the road
in no time.

15:27.437 --> 15:30.109
JOY: To where?

15:30.109 --> 15:31.737
‐ The Laughing Place,
of course.

15:31.737 --> 15:34.200
‐ Where?
Montreal, still?

15:34.200 --> 15:37.206
ANNIE: Why not?

15:37.206 --> 15:39.168
