you needed temp RNs.

16:00.127 --> 16:01.797
‐ Okay, you on any medications?

16:01.797 --> 16:04.218
‐ No.
JAMAL: State screening.

16:04.218 --> 16:06.097
Now even temp RNs have to list.

16:06.097 --> 16:08.644
Annie: Oh, well, vitamin D.

16:08.644 --> 16:12.151
