the vitamin D, right?

16:12.151 --> 16:15.700
Okay, then, just need
two forms of ID, Ms. Ingalls.

16:19.625 --> 16:21.044
‐ Birth certificate.

16:21.044 --> 16:23.966
It's a copy.
I hope that's okay.

16:25.970 --> 16:29.143
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

16:29.143 --> 16:32.651
