<i>we get all the greatest hits.</i>

16:34.488 --> 16:37.953
<i>Appendicitis, vaccines,</i>
<i>arrhythmias.</i>

16:37.953 --> 16:41.084
Intakes from Castle Rock,
you're looking at 70‐80% ODs.

16:41.084 --> 16:43.714
All NARCAN all the time.

16:43.714 --> 16:46.804
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:46.804 --> 16:49.351
[marker squeaking]

16:49.351 --> 16:50.895
