nurse practitioners
have the passcode.

16:52.816 --> 16:54.403
‐ Seems like a lot
of extra work.

16:54.403 --> 16:57.742
‐ Mm, new state regs
'cause of all the damn junkies.

16:57.742 --> 17:00.999
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:00.999 --> 17:03.963
