17:30.808 --> 17:32.061
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:32.061 --> 17:34.190
<i>[keypad beeps, echoes]</i>

17:34.190 --> 17:35.943
NURSE: Anne?

17:35.943 --> 17:37.656
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:37.656 --> 17:39.951
