17:39.951 --> 17:41.329
<i>[monitor beeping]</i>
<i>[clanging continues]</i>

17:41.329 --> 17:43.584
<i>[paddles charging]</i>

17:43.584 --> 17:45.755
<i>[monitor beeps]</i>

